## Third-Party Libraries

This project uses the following open-source libraries:

### MFRC522 Library
- **License**: Public Domain / Unlicense
- **Author**: Miguel Balboa and contributors
- **URL**: https://github.com/miguelbalboa/rfid

### DFRobotDFPlayerMini Library  
- **License**: MIT License
- **Author**: DFRobot and contributors
- **URL**: https://github.com/DFRobot/DFRobotDFPlayerMini

### ESPAsyncWebServer Library
- **License**: LGPL-3.0 License
- **Author**: Otto Winter and contributors  
- **URL**: https://github.com/ottowinter/ESPAsyncWebServer-esphome

### ESP32 Arduino Core
- **License**: LGPL-2.1 License
- **Author**: Espressif Systems
